THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN ENERGY HEALING CERTIFICATIONS

Certification programs are completed online at your own pace during the six-month timeline and include hands-on practice sessions.

The Emotion Code

Level 1 Certification

  • Is a pre-requisite for further education with The Body Code
  • Focuses on learning how to identify and release trapped emotions
  • Course emphasizes learning how to resolve a Heart-Wall®

The Body Code

Level 2 Certification

  • This certification takes your understanding deeper for expert-level mastery
  • The course focuses on understanding the 6 main imbalance types
  • Perfecting muscle testing techniques is emphasized throughout the course
  • To enroll in this course you must first complete Level 1: The Emotion Code, and have a subscription to The Body Code System

EMOTION CODE COURSE REQUIREMENTS

The Emotion Code Certification Program is self-paced within the six-month course timeline and can be done entirely online. Many students finish the course within just six to eight weeks. You will have a student advisor from Discover Healing assigned to help you, answer your questions, and review your work as you are learning.

Review our Emotion Code Certification Success Plan for a timeline that will help you
complete your course material and practice sessions in just 10 weeks!

During the engaging online course you will:

  • Learn methods and techniques for muscle testing, to tap into your subconscious knowledge.

  • Gain a complete understanding of how to identify and release Heart-Walls® and trapped emotions.

  • Learn through 10 engaging learning modules, complete with videos, quizzes, and readings from The Emotion Code book.

  • Hands-on experience performing energy healing sessions, including sessions on yourself, on others, and animals!

Enroll Now!

*Certification course requirements must be submitted within 6 months (183 days) of purchase. After that time, students will need to purchase Course Re-enrollment in order to complete certification.

**You must be 18 years of age or older to participate in any certification programs with Discover Healing.

BODY CODE CERTIFICATION REQUIREMENTS

The Body Code Certification Program is self-paced within the six-month course timeline and can be done entirely online. Many students finish the course within just six to eight weeks. You will have a student advisor from Discover Healing assigned to help you, answer your questions, and review your work as you are learning.

You must complete Level 1 Certification: The Emotion Code® before enrolling in this program and a subscription to The Body Code System or previous purchase of Body Code System is also required.

Review our Body Code Certification Success Plan for a timeline that will help you
complete your course material and practice sessions in just 10 weeks!

During the virtual course you will:

  • Build on topics and skills learned in the Emotion Code® for expert-level mastery.

  • Explore the six types of imbalances and their subcategories in depth.

  • Enjoy 10 engaging learning modules, complete with videos and demonstrations by Dr. Brad, Jean, and Josh.

  • Learn how to identify and release the root causes of suffering in the body, mind, and spirit so you can help anyone, anywhere!

  • Gain experience performing energy healing sessions, including sessions on yourself, on others, and animals.

Enroll Now!

**You must be 18 years of age or older to participate in any certification programs with Discover Healing.
